{"title":"Pielonefritis Flegmonosa","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Infectología/Pielonefritis Flegmonosa.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Pielonefritis\\NFlegmonosa","guid":"2zUQmydKSN6YFRd-Ci9wIA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definicion y\\NConceptos","guid":"q01hkjjoRaaulku4EGAg_g","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Infeccion supurativa del parenquima renal con INFLAMACION DIFUSA sin licuefaccion franca","guid":"136WUCtcS9Kc3PV0rUSMjQ","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Espectro continuo de infeccion renal complicada","guid":"pEoYwqK5Tf6UUULxClMn9w","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"PNA no complicada → Nefritis bacteriana focal (lobar nephronia) → Absceso renal → Pionefrosis","guid":"s_YyhCEjRh-MHrxS99ROaQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Terminos sinonimos y relacionados","guid":"iyZ-dCkRSjuA0btne9nnCQ","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"Nefritis bacteriana focal aguda (AFBN) = Nefronia lobar aguda","guid":"53pYLYURT_mADyC_AK2xtw","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"Descrita por Rosenfield et al. 1979","guid":"3WMvN4qWT6OLNhjsGIxqmg","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"5","text":"Lesion inflamatoria solida SIN licuefaccion ni formacion de absceso","guid":"UpsH30VVThWR2L5qH8UXGA","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"Formas graves del espectro","guid":"qF7pSL5aTKmHsB7K4JhAYw","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Pielonefritis enfisematosa → infeccion necrotizante formadora de gas","guid":"mcJlid_BSdivg8whLLZw0g","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"Pielonefritis xantogranulomatosa → destruccion cronica con macrofagos espumosos","guid":"fxr-Q5sXS5mfL2iMUeI82g","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"Absceso renal → coleccion purulenta intrarrenal","guid":"TogxHyTJSXSbBoVR6-b2ag","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"9","text":"Absceso perinefrico → extension mas alla de capsula renal","guid":"LrMTHoUJSvu8iUFMN-YJUw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiologia","guid":"i3UZELJ-QRGTfmjPUIsE2Q","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"PNA: 459,000-1,138,000 casos anuales en EE.UU.","guid":"SvG8vO_SRyK1RmQsUIlwPQ","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"Hospitalizacion mayor en >65 anos y ninos pequenos","guid":"tOcerHcsRwmzdWBd52a-qA","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"AFBN → mayoria mujeres (~82%), edad media 47 anos","guid":"boxO-wLBS8WHoWpV4IEEKg","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"Bacteriemia en PNA: <10% a >50% segun factores del huesped","guid":"fMViI4LdSgGscsd8M9QlpA","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"14","text":"Pielonefritis enfisematosa → mortalidad ~38%","guid":"y5OtmlVNSPSmXzr5x9OMyw","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"14","text":"Incidencia abscesos renales: 1-10/10,000 ingresos hospitalarios","guid":"9PmQ-xh5R5maIjAsMpLXNQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"0","text":"Factores de Riesgo","guid":"sW1gU_FkSW2qkKwIqs9B8w","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"DIABETES MELLITUS → factor clave en formas complicadas","guid":"S7KVP8lDTvydn9Uci3oDyw","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Mayor riesgo de enfisematosa, necrosis papilar, abscesos","guid":"IgtzdcR0Q5Wcv3ogGmbu7g","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"Obstruccion del tracto urinario","guid":"SJPdsIEWT_axh2zes2O-FQ","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"Urolitiasis, tumores, hiperplasia prostatica","guid":"cN_HYXqRRRKTRM1iuOiCRA","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"21","text":"Inmunosupresion","guid":"fvxzID-VQGieXqQxorJSiQ","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Trasplante renal → PNA en 30-50% primeros 2 meses","guid":"LoeE9_RjToe4waiR92OcwQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"21","text":"Anomalias urologicas estructurales o funcionales","guid":"0j6F69GdS8OrmRGx46P5Pg","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"21","text":"Edad >65 anos → presentaciones atipicas","guid":"4dYdGQqCTISlj2S2DrlaVw","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"21","text":"Enfermedad de celulas falciformes","guid":"XKDsAnlJRkuwhJENrrlcSg","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"21","text":"Uso prolongado de cateter urinario → infeccion polimicrobiana","guid":"OlnrlkXBTgGsN1WmE0l7pw","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"21","text":"pH urinario >=7.0","guid":"Z_4AlKrVSt6dF20sfe1CBg","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"0","text":"Microbiologia","guid":"WT2oOSkrTqK1okMckcQuvA","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"E. coli → 70-90% de los casos","guid":"2uBb2ND_Q_CMeRxI787t2g","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"Cepas virulentas con fimbrias P (adhesion uroepitelial)","guid":"_p85-2RkRlOt4K3rqyJcdQ","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"Clon ST131 subconjunto H30 → RESISTENCIA emergente","guid":"lQUMZwgMS0ii_dJfuOkYsQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"33","text":"Klebsiella pneumoniae → segundo agente mas frecuente","guid":"3ctUq6N8R9WvPxQJdPQVsQ","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"Asociada a enfisematosa junto con E. coli","guid":"NHVf7ff1SI6WOI4_24a4Zg","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"33","text":"Proteus mirabilis","guid":"1o5UfKtbQGS1-fgZTh0Alw","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"33","text":"Enterococcus spp → mas frecuente en hospitalizados/institucionalizados","guid":"9igmgyA7RxCv1R0OcL4Juw","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"33","text":"Staphylococcus aureus → via hematogena","guid":"Rq7kt-xIRUq4A_8UOv5Gqg","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"33","text":"Candida spp → via hematogena, inmunodeprimidos","guid":"wLOS2979SUOLLUdDP42lNg","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"33","text":"Pseudomonas aeruginosa → asociado a cateter/instrumentacion","guid":"k3br9D2ORlOuyB0BZQsqoA","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"33","text":"Infecciones polimicrobianas → mas comunes con cateter >50%","guid":"pn_ximATSveD6YzahB71rw","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"0","text":"Patogenia","guid":"7P_eP34FT8eeccBTGiilAw","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"Via ascendente → PRINCIPAL","guid":"aw6Mea2xQM-rhGi_RtqpPg","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Bacterias entericas → vejiga → ascenso a rinon","guid":"0B0zOXQuSSGZMys5wFIB7g","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"Factores de virulencia: fimbrias P, formacion de biofilm","guid":"nv6oOUyDQHKWsGF8e9bm-w","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"45","text":"Via hematogena → RARA","guid":"DhFGFkcpRZ2qk7BOO_AG0A","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"S. aureus, Candida","guid":"R-Vjqag8R3yK82ERWQ4RGQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"45","text":"Progresion del dano renal","guid":"SqDlS8WbTOa6f_RBNDI9yw","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"PNA → infiltracion neutrofilica difusa → microabscesos","guid":"Bt3pWxSyS3uQwq0f0tbxHA","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"AFBN → necrosis focal NO licuefactiva → lesion solida inflamatoria","guid":"gJd_2mQER-mS9UugUvHTiA","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"51","text":"Absceso renal → licuefaccion y coleccion purulenta","guid":"ocy5lM7XTS6X24ZcQ__V4g","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"51","text":"Absceso perinefrico → extension a espacio perirrenal","guid":"2Z-YgPlYS2CX42yHcIwE9Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"45","text":"Enfisematosa → fermentacion de glucosa por bacterias formadoras de gas","guid":"dHNmmuATQTuFYFzrpoVMCQ","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"45","text":"Xantogranulomatosa → inflamacion granulomatosa cronica con macrofagos cargados de lipidos","guid":"n0VW0dUITT6oDaLrWcXooA","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"45","text":"Cicatrizacion → deposito de colageno reemplaza tejido funcional","guid":"IDMLPh3IQfa2mSJW5mDQcA","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"0","text":"Presentacion Clinica","guid":"kVVavgq0ToKa3OzeTSqX-Q","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"Triada clasica: fiebre + dolor lumbar + nauseas/vomitos","guid":"fy124tiETviV12bD31iqNQ","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"HASTA 20% sin sintomas vesicales","guid":"6iSIgquYQjW6644uaKOi1A","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"Algunos sin fiebre","guid":"ZBqBQXGATG2nqcNhSSvvJA","children":[]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"59","text":"AFBN vs PNA → clinicamente INDISTINGUIBLES","guid":"i3vQFNBTT8OlyP1ozL9ZYQ","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"Sospecha si fiebre persiste >=4 dias con ATB adecuado","guid":"mt3OBQY4QkKqJmjjPkKe6A","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"Temperatura pico ~39.3 grados C","guid":"t2M6jpaMR9mBiASYhGQXWA","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"59","text":"Bacteriemia en AFBN → solo ~6.3%","guid":"g3eP1eNISduKhHNKCjSNOw","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"59","text":"Adulto mayor → PRESENTACION ATIPICA","guid":"TYxBJ_bGQmWWjaSUg4kD8w","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"Delirium como unica manifestacion","guid":"zNwfefmFSVOnJS-zqubyNQ","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"Deterioro funcional agudo","guid":"7ad5hq9JQM-ZnxUWv_oPSg","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"Caida sin causa aparente","guid":"3vGn0l7ATFWxHGkQVYYQgw","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"67","text":"Taquicardia sin fiebre","guid":"d9gVruQEQme3ANaruQxhMQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"59","text":"Enfisematosa → sepsis severa, crepitacion en flanco (raro)","guid":"vmLoU9xrT6Om6ILHvviuCQ","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"59","text":"Xantogranulomatosa → fiebre recurrente, masa renal dolorosa, anemia","guid":"_8EoCByYSBiDPwNgBAkmSA","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"59","text":"Complicaciones","guid":"Xe9bSsftTOyCMNTEeokkJw","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"Sepsis y shock septico","guid":"Qhuim0nmRFSVJtid7yDhxA","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"Lesion renal aguda","guid":"W8chxYEZQPOaCf79CvIUcg","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"74","text":"Necrosis papilar","guid":"uBHZeg8ITDiYDOMMmF9nDA","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"74","text":"Pionefrosis (obstructiva) → EMERGENCIA","guid":"OarQnoN6RcGP1BRYWQIzDQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"0","text":"Diagnostico","guid":"LW6azQynQJ2P-g-ZHzmsZA","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"Laboratorio","guid":"OCrxY9twQpeTHRcmNSipvQ","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"Urocultivo → CARDINAL → >=10,000 UFC/mL","guid":"ajJjSTUQTOqW3ih6U4Uwfw","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"Urinalisis → piuria, bacteriuria, nitritos","guid":"cNMcR-R3S2O5hzsL6LC6-g","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"Sensibilidad combinada (LE + nitritos) 75-84%","guid":"LRDw-nzTRTuhIiUvF8tzww","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"Especificidad 82-98%","guid":"v2b_6LPNSpmaguDUWgqwqQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"80","text":"Hemocultivos → utiles en ambiguos, inmunodeprimidos, hematogena","guid":"ebPhaXPgTkGgqwCHTQ274A","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"80","text":"PCR y PCT elevadas → AFBN tiene marcadores mas altos que PNA no complicada","guid":"Iv9weG-CSMWs_XVTaScDkw","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"80","text":"Leucocitosis con neutrofilia","guid":"oIbm6s7EQB6XnBsVGxKJ3g","children":[]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"79","text":"Imagenologia","guid":"q3mG6LcZQJWgFDDHzvxSXQ","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"Indicaciones de imagen INMEDIATA","guid":"CPHL5KCTRP6eIhqp9sw7fA","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"Sepsis o shock septico","guid":"VnPmdwhwSXSgxGQ5Q_3h5Q","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"Urolitiasis conocida o sospechada","guid":"RyXid3LeQPqrSk6l1YITkg","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"89","text":"pH urinario >=7.0","guid":"Nn6a9yXFQAGBO8yzum_aEg","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"89","text":"Disminucion nueva de TFG a <=40 mL/min","guid":"wvnz1lNaTSKYrBSJtHnNnA","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"88","text":"Imagen si NO MEJORA en 24-48h de ATB","guid":"XNIhkz6OQiqx2BklqXI-rg","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"88","text":"TC con contraste → GOLD STANDARD para complicaciones","guid":"MqzFjvUXRqSwfFlhbF1UKg","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"AFBN → area hipodensa cuniforme con pobre 